{"tid":2417340,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[sos求攻略]win7卡關解決唔到svchost.exe無限復活","createTime":"2021-02-21T20:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T23:28:31.000Z","uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2683c3e3c49a37dbe5440e312e3c73c90ba9b74b","tid":2417340,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T20:48:44.000Z","msg":"利申: 某d原因下必須幫舊機重裝win7(sp1), 任何野都fine, 唯獨粒cpu由1開始到永遠都half load 50%以上, 瘋狂執行緊1個叫svchost.exe既仆街, 研究左幾日網上d解法, 但冇任何方法有用, 最後我personally獨創左某種麻煩d既方式暫時解決, <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求1勞永逸既解法, 感激各位大佬&amp;曾擊殺svchost既成功人士<br />\n<br />\n機體資訊補充: 各種野正常, cpu係i5 3570, 顯卡係radeon hd7950 vaporX, 底板係gigabyte GA-H77M-D3H, ram 8+8g 1600mhz ddr3<br />\n<br />\n軟件資訊補充: 1開機, 共有16件svchost.exe大家族run緊, 網上話咁係正常, 而16件之1既svchost.exe會食住50% cpu, 終止左佢後唔會有任何error或效能變差乜乜物物, 係完全冇壞影響, cpu會即刻正常返(見圖), 問題係終止完條仆街會原地滿血復活, 無論用咩方法, 只要終止左佢, 佢都會滿血復活<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJSLRMW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJSLRMW.png&h=ad8c788f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NmuRNkg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNmuRNkg.jpg&h=8e13bf40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&darr;試過解法1 <span class=\"red\">[作用0%] </span><br />\n網上99.99%解決都係叫你停BIT同win update, 當然唔影響條仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocFQ2Uw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocFQ2Uw.jpg&h=a8f6e7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ThABd1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FThABd1b.jpg&h=69837581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OOyCHUw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOOyCHUw.jpg&h=3d1aac2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&darr;試過解法2 <span class=\"red\">[作用0%] </span><br />\n咁就咁click終止咪得? 任何情況下終止完(cpu50%&rarr;0%)後72秒就會(cpu0%&rarr;50%)原地滿血復活, 重新出現, 唔同既只係佢個PID<br />\n<br />\n&darr;試過解法3 <span class=\"red\">[作用0%] </span><br />\n離線win7更新, 更到2020年最新版, 當然條仆街wfc繼續食cpu, 同場加映佢多左個契弟mscorsvw.exe食埋剩返50%cpu, 即係1開機就100%cpu咩都唔做都100%直至熄機, <a href=\"http://只係佢個契弟mscorsvw.exe原來係.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%AA%E4%BF%82%E4%BD%A2%E5%80%8B%E5%A5%91%E5%BC%9Fmscorsvw.exe%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E4%BF%82.net&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=15768423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">只係佢個契弟mscorsvw.exe原來係.net</a> frame x86係我部64仆元win7執行先出事, <a href=\"http://永久停止左個.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%B7%A6%E5%80%8B.net&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=ded14bf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">永久停止左個.net</a> frame x86服務可完美解決個契弟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZZ2T2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZZ2T2A.jpg&h=817c7c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n試過解法4 <span class=\"red\">[作用0%] </span><br />\n線上更新win7, 更到冇得再更, 新到冇得再新, 當然條仆街dont give a shit<br />\n<br />\n試過解法5 <span class=\"red\">[作用0%] </span><br />\n跟住試埋d偏方, 例如重新註冊windows update登錄檔<br />\n又例如del C:\\WINDOWS\\SoftwareDistribution 入面d垃圾<br />\n又例如開eventvwr清晒windows logs<br />\n<br />\n治標不治本個人方法 <span class=\"green\">[作用100]</span><br />\n既然終止唔到, 殺完又會再生, 就唯有暫停佢, 1黎佢run唔到2黎再生唔到, 但幾麻煩, 要每次開機都要做1次先, 故求真正解法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9YuBYxw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9YuBYxw.png&h=399e38a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc9ea063c67472f99c59e0fb589362b1c1e142df","tid":2417340,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T20:58:05.000Z","msg":"樓上last張圖係同條仆街有關既登錄檔(唔關佢另外15個兄弟姊妹事, 淨係食cpu條仆街), 我認為好可能係其中某d服務透過個svchost loop緊d垃圾指令<br />\n<br />\n利申: 應該唔關我個防毒avast事, avast淨係開緊檔案保護+動作保護, 停左呢2樣野後, 條仆街依然係度, 而其他果d關連服務真係唔識分邊d正常邊d出事, <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sos"},{"pid":"4fc913919bd68f6f6fd988f96ef252b7d55aafd7","tid":2417340,"uid":34147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T21:01:33.000Z","msg":"其實 svchost 係一個 container<br />\n好睇你入邊包住嘅係啲乜嘢行<br />\n有時hardware 都會影響到<br />\n如果捉咗大半日鬼都捉唔到係咩問題嘅話<br />\n最簡單去安全模式試<br />\n安全模式都有問題嘅話就九成hadware 問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0927ec4fdc52f8e2fb71424a71427901d9500ea1","tid":2417340,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fc913919bd68f6f6fd988f96ef252b7d55aafd7","tid":2417340,"uid":34147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T21:01:33.000Z","msg":"其實 svchost 係一個 container<br />\n好睇你入邊包住嘅係啲乜嘢行<br />\n有時hardware 都會影響到<br />\n如果捉咗大半日鬼都捉唔到係咩問題嘅話<br />\n最簡單去安全模式試<br />\n安全模式都有問題嘅話就九成hadware 問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T21:10:48.000Z","msg":"svchost個原理其實我都了解過, 即係收order辦事, 佢入面包住d咩我經已完整list晒出黎<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KNq19K8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKNq19K8.png&h=a9cbc866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但冇辦法, 我終止內面其中任何1條服務, 即係「\\BaseNameObjects]到[\\REGISTRY\\.....]呢堆, 個svchost.exe都會同步終止, 然後會再次重生, 佢d服務內容會1樣<br />\n<br />\n我估要直接搵到問題源頭, 先斷左源頭俾svchost既指令先得, 只係我搞唔掂果堆服務, 唔明佢地做緊咩or邊度出問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb95551b628aebac2c38a435a49fd2e203932029","tid":2417340,"uid":122471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T21:12:18.000Z","msg":"至於安全模式, 安全模式可以點到個問題出黎? <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee65cd97d05517be482ba5bd1aa06b24546f8a91","tid":2417340,"uid":122471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T21:17:24.000Z","msg":"而據我所知, 由winXP 到 win10, 都1直存在緊svchost.exe食cpu或ram既問題 (病毒感染果d唔計, 就係就咁正常系統程序都經已出事)<br />\n<br />\n希望可以參考到1d成功例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d3db2a81b5857443b9efbd1b5e8a9c25d5a500","tid":2417340,"ui